# Styling & Party Theme

## Theme Colors (defined in globals.css)
Custom party colors available as Tailwind classes:
- `text-party-pink`, `bg-party-pink` — vibrant pink
- `text-party-purple`, `bg-party-purple` — deep purple (also `--primary`)
- `text-party-orange`, `bg-party-orange` — warm orange
- `text-party-yellow`, `bg-party-yellow` — bright yellow
- `text-party-green`, `bg-party-green` — fresh green
- `text-party-blue`, `bg-party-blue` — sky blue

## Gradient Utilities
- `.party-gradient` — full vibrant gradient (pink → purple → blue → green) for CTAs and icons
- `.party-gradient-soft` — muted version for backgrounds

## Typography
- `font-heading` (Poppins) — headings, titles, emphasis
- `font-sans` (Inter) — body text, inherited by default

## Conventions
- Use `rounded-2xl` or `rounded-full` for playful feel
- Buttons use `party-gradient text-white font-semibold` for primary actions
- Cards use shadcn `Card` with subtle hover (`hover:shadow-md hover:-translate-y-1`)
- Use Framer Motion `motion.div` for entrance animations on pages
